---
title: Crumbed Chicken Strip Tacos with Charred Pineapple Salsa & Zesty Slaw
description: Chicken tacos, it can’t get any better. Oh wait, it can because we’re crumbing these chicken strips with a smokey Aussie spice mix. Top them with a pineapple salsa and these tacos are very hard to beat.
